---
import BaseSlide from './BaseSlide.astro';
---

<BaseSlide id="inspiration" title="Вдохновение">
  <div class="space-y-6 text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-300">
    <p>Вдохновился я на нынешний доклад после прочтения статьи:</p>

    <div
      class="bg-blue-950/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors"
    >
      <a
        href="https://react.dev/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-semibold text-xl flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        You Might Not Need an Effect
        <span class="text-sm">↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="pt-4">
      Также по теме может быть полезно почитать непосредственно саму доку React:
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 pl-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span>
        <a
          href="https://react.dev/learn/synchronizing-with-effects"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline"
        >
          Synchronizing with Effects
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span>
        <a
          href="https://react.dev/learn/separating-events-from-effects"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline"
        >
          Separating Events from Effects
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span>
        <a
          href="https://react.dev/learn/lifecycle-of-reactive-effects"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 hover:underline"
        >
          Lifecycle of Reactive Effects
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseSlide>
